{"id":1546,"date":"2022-11-04T12:13:25","date_gmt":"2022-11-04T16:13:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1546"},"modified":"2023-07-26T09:46:01","modified_gmt":"2023-07-26T13:46:01","slug":"guillaume-dupuis","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/guillaume-dupuis\/","title":{"rendered":"Guillaume Dupuis"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span class=\"TextRun Highlight SCXW187105605 BCX0\" lang=\"FR-CA\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\" data-contrast=\"none\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">Guillaume <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">est titulaire d\u2019une ma\u00eetrise en <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">cin\u00e9ma<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">\u202f<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">de l\u2019Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">. Il a eu la chance d\u2019enseigner le cin\u00e9ma dans <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">diff\u00e9rents <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">c\u00e9gep<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">s<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\"> (Saint-Hyacinthe, Rosemont et Ahuntsic) avant de se poser, en 2017, au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent. Il adore le cin\u00e9ma de John Cassavetes, de Chantal Akerman, de Jacques Rivette\u202fet\u202fd\u2019Ernst Lubitsh\u202f(pour ne nommer que ceux-l\u00e0).\u202fIl se passionne pour les diff\u00e9rents cin\u00e9mas nationaux et leur histoire, pour le cin\u00e9ma documentaire et\u202fle cin\u00e9ma exp\u00e9rimental, tout en se fascinant pour la question de l\u2019acteur de cin\u00e9ma\u202fet pour les cin\u00e9astes qui laissent \u00e0 ces derniers une place centrale dans le processus de cr\u00e9ation d\u2019une\u202f\u0153uvre.\u202fIl garde soigneusement en m\u00e9moire ce que\u202fCassavetes disait\u202f: \u00ab \u2026nous n\u2019aurions jamais pu finir si tous ceux qui participaient au film\u202fn\u2019avaient d\u00e9couvert cet \u00e9l\u00e9ment absolument fondamental\u202f: que le fait d\u2019\u00eatre artiste, ce n\u2019est\u202frien d\u2019autre que le d\u00e9sir, la volont\u00e9 forcen\u00e9e d\u2019une expression compl\u00e8te, absolue de soi-m\u00eam<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW187105605 BCX0\">e \u00bb.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW187105605 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2291,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[276],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1546","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-cinema"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1546","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2291"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1546"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=1546"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=1546"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=1546"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=1546"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}